	<article class="post-554918 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-hedge-funds tag-berkshire-hathaway-inc tag-buffett-warren-e tag-kass-douglas-a tag-seabreeze-partners-management tag-stocks-and-bonds per-buffett-warren-e des-stocks-and-bonds org-berkshire-hathaway-inc org-seabreeze-partners-management nyt_request_per-kass-douglas-a" id="post-554918">
