<div id="addendums" class="addendums"><div class="story-addendum theme-correction"><strong>Correction: March 4, 2013</strong> <br>An earlier version of this article misstated Doug Kass's investment position in Berkshire Hathaway. He is shorting the stock; it is not the case that he was "not currently" short the company's shares.</div></div><footer class="story-footer">
